<h2 id="results">Results</h2>

<p>
The final output are segmented spots with corresponding gene identity in an easy 
to process plain text file. 
</p>

<h3>Secondary Analysis Software</h3>
<p>
Our interactive analysis software helps to perform subsequent data analysis such as
quantification (counting), and it helps to project results back into the images,
either highlighting individual transcripts, combinations of genes or whole gene-sets
to map transcription patterns onto morphological structures.
A colocalization matrix is determined and presented as a dendrogram or heatmap.
Results can be exported in publication-ready quality.
</p>

