<h3>Community Software</h3>
<p>
Intersections with regions of interest, such as cell-boundaries or other spatial domains, 
yield data in formats compatible with standard downstream bioinformatic tools that are 
commonly applied to characterize and cluster single cells based on transcription profiles.
We will provide example datasets and tutorials to demonstrate how standard tools can help 
to interpret your data.
</p>

